35:32.305 --> 35:40.112
beach, taking a crap out there in about a foot of 
water and expecting the tide to take it out. And I

35:40.933 --> 35:43.035
guess it did, because they kept on doing it. It was 
amazing. So, you know, what kind of people are you

35:45.798 --> 35:50.442
talking about?

35:52.844 --> 36:00.912
So, you know, did the people ever even, were they 
aware of... of what was going on in their country.

36:07.035 --> 36:09.738
People like that are not well-informed. They 
don't know politics.

36:14.183 --> 36:26.315
I'm sure they were aware that their whole country 
has been a war-torn country for as long as they can

36:14.183 --> 36:26.315
remember and generations back, but they don't 
know why. Probably didn't care. They don't care.

36:30.659 --> 36:37.225
If they had their fish and their rice for three 
meals a day or two meals a day, they'd be perfectly

36:30.659 --> 36:37.225
satisfied.

