yes, I did. I think that anything that has two legs 
and stands upright and can carry on a

37:11.934 --> 37:27.430
conversation, no matter how deep that 
conversation can be as a human being, and it's a

37:11.934 --> 37:27.430
damn shame that things like that do go on in the 
