37:28.237 --> 37:54.835
okay when you flew medevac what effect did, seeing 
all the death and destruction of

37:55.490 --> 38:04.962
US soldiers, what effect did that have on you? And 
how did you deal with it?

38:10.369 --> 38:18.240
Well, it

38:10.369 --> 38:18.240
has to have an effect on anyone, I'm sure. How much 
you let it affect you is another thing. I think I can

38:24.970 --> 38:52.564
consider myself as lucky as being one of the kind of 
people, I don't think I'm a hard person, really and

38:24.970 --> 38:52.564
truly I think I'm a pretty soft-hearted person, 
but

38:24.970 --> 38:52.564
something like that, I was fortunate enough to be 
able to somewhat disconnect myself from, and I

38:24.970 --> 38:52.564
think it He had a lot to do with my first flight in 
country, which I was relating to earlier. I wish

