39:27.669 --> 39:36.981
extracts, or extract this many people. And during 
which time, we had to refuel. And so we went into

39:43.229 --> 39:48.876
Dong Ha to refuel. And we were sitting there 
refueling, and this pilot was sitting there, and

39:49.278 --> 40:02.937
he looked over at me and just started laughing, and 
he started cracking jokes. And I was puzzled by

40:02.957 --> 40:17.277
what he was doing, and later he told me that the only 
way that he could cope with what he was doing out

40:02.957 --> 40:17.277
there and seeing what he was seeing was to... 
lighten up and take his mind off of it and think

40:17.780 --> 40:46.032
about something else crack a joke or anything and I

40:17.780 --> 40:46.032
can't remember what his worries were that's a 
number of years ago but it hung with me and I think me

40:17.780 --> 40:46.032
being with him during that first date of first day 
of turmoil and tragedy that I saw prepared me for

40:47.176 --> 40:48.758
the rest of the year. And it let me shrug off some of 
this, detach myself from it, and not get

40:49.639 --> 41:01.191
personally involved. There was one fellow that I 
